span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c42c836ea3b79d6ea22ef75902bdc3c3edeb9c95","tid":1631353,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bab0f557cef8c9a79b932907c9bc65fc78edfdab","tid":1631353,"uid":271250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"咁大個人都唔化，唔洗驗都知你蠢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"但我駁唔到我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋主要係好奇"},{"pid":"e8758f48675a19439489eeb77e0256fa689a62e5","tid":1631353,"uid":271250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c42c836ea3b79d6ea22ef75902bdc3c3edeb9c95","tid":1631353,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bab0f557cef8c9a79b932907c9bc65fc78edfdab","tid":1631353,"uid":271250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"咁大個人都唔化，唔洗驗都知你蠢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"但我駁唔到我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋主要係好奇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:31:52.000Z","msg":"過左成年好似唔得驗的，因為教育，環境等因素，影響個test唔準"}]}